    "description_long": "This is a compact, low-profile sports car with a striking red body and a matte black hood and roof. The car features a prominent rear spoiler, enhancing its aerodynamic appearance, and wide, low-profile tires mounted on multi-spoke alloy wheels. The windows are tinted dark, and the car has a two-door coupe design with a streamlined, angular silhouette. The front end is equipped with rectangular headlights and a subtle grille, while the rear showcases angular taillights and a large rear bumper. Side mirrors are mounted on both doors, and the overall design emphasizes speed and agility, typical of urban performance vehicles.",
